<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge" />
  </head>
  <body
    style="
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: white;
      height: fit-content;
      font-family: 'Franklin Gothic Medium', 'Arial Narrow', Arial, sans-serif;
      width: 100%
    "
  >
    <div
      style="
        width: 75%;
        background-color: #070c1d;
      "
    >
      <div
        style="
          font-family: 'Franklin Gothic Medium', 'Arial Narrow', Arial,
            sans-serif;
          padding: 15px 20px;
          background-color: #363636;
          font-size: 25px;
          display: flex;
          align-items: center;
          letter-spacing: 1px;
        "
      >
        Event Managers
      </div>
      <div
        style="
          padding: 20px;
          width: 100%;
        "
      >
        <div style="display: flex; width: 100%">
          <div
            style="height: 75px; width: 75px; margin: auto; margin-bottom: 10px"
          >
            <img
              src={{committeeLogo}}
              style="
                height: 100%;
                width: 100%;
                object-fit: contain;
                object-position: center;
              "
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <h2
          style="
            font-family: 'Franklin Gothic Medium', 'Arial Narrow', Arial,
              sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            width: 40%;
            margin: auto;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
          "
        >
          {{header}}
        </h2>
        <div
          style="
            height: 250px;
            width: 90%;
            margin: auto;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
          "
        >
          <img
            src={{eventBanner}}
            style="
              height: 100%;
              width: 100%;
              object-fit: contain;
              object-position: center;
            "
          />
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="padding: 10px 30px">
        <div
          style="
          "
        >
          <h2
            style="
              font-size: 20px;
            "
          >
            {{eventName}}
          </h2>
          <p>{{eventDate}}</p>
        </div>
        <div style="font-weight: lighter">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Quis nobis
          atque veniam magni tempora ad. Eveniet architecto numquam optio
          accusamus nisi unde earum, similique, vel laboriosam ad, saepe minima
          quos.
        </div>
        <a
          href={{eventLink}}
          style="display:inline-block; margin: 15px 0; "
        >Click here to view more details</a>
      </div>
      <div style="height: 20px; background-color: #363636; width: 100%"></div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>